==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stepped
<hw>Stepped</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Provided with a step
or steps; having a series of offsets or parts resembling the steps of
stairs; <as>as, a <ex>stepped</ex> key</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Stepped gear</b></col>, <cd>a cogwheel of which the teeth
cross the face in a series of steps.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stepper</ent>⟦br⟧
